{"tid":2448451,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A/PC】夢幻模擬戰 (59) 繼續咸魚","createTime":"2021-03-16T02:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T01:15:26.000Z","uid":35891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"30293fcf94b864556776d2a3cee9dfb30bb13955","tid":2448451,"uid":35891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnibWoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnibWoX.jpg&h=b7053167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZX1scuq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX1scuq.png&h=22d004fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Chym1nK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChym1nK.png&h=a0dbc157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://mz.game-beans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmz.game-beans.com&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=94b7bc7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://mz.game-beans.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">首抽開局推介:</span><br />\n越出越多角色  每個陣營需要既核心角色都唔同<br />\n有疑問直接留言問巴打<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">新手 FAQ:</span><br />\n<span class=\"pink\">Q: 陣營有乜用?</span><br />\nA: 遊戲角色分各大陣營(之後會出更多)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYeZkRz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYeZkRz.png&h=b60fed0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABTvswB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABTvswB.png&h=e2aa2275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2j224Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2j224Y.png&h=93f04652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCx0PK0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCx0PK0.png&h=066ff95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpMXRYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpMXRYn.png&h=6330a69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vx0tYDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvx0tYDp.png&h=ea8492b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfTCRYr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfTCRYr.png&h=6caad36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYdLgp8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYdLgp8.png&h=fa2d8d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qgwg7wQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgwg7wQ.png&h=4ffb65ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmwADDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmwADDx.png&h=defcfa2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6VE5iG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6VE5iG.png&h=9efc18dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xrGteb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxrGteb2.png&h=a30e9562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n35級後有超絕buff要同陣營先食到(攻擊智力防+20% 魔防+30%)唔同超絕再有唔同額外效果<br />\n所以建議培養同陣營角色方便食到超絕buff<br />\n由於資源有限 <strong>強烈建議初期集中玩一個陣營</strong><br />\n但新手對陣營通常都會理解唔到  <br />\n唔刷首抽就三主角+光輝玩起<br />\n真係唔知點揀，一係抽左角再決定<br />\n一係上黎問問巴打們<span class=\"pink\"></span><br />\n<span class=\"pink\">Q: 新手點升Rank好?</span><br />\nA: 1體=1經 組隊有折扣   前期建議組隊刷兄貴<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">Q: 卡關點算?</span><br />\nA: 強化裝備 SR照突破升  拆左會退返錢同槌仔比你<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">Q: 職業材料好少點算?</span><br />\nA: 喺世界頻搵公會收留，用旅團點換<br />\n活人好搶手，唔怕冇人要<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">Q: SSR裝點拎?</span><br />\nA: 打40級以上龍每日獎勵有機率出<br />\n冇每日獎勵50級以上<br />\n星期一、四：火龍(除飾品咩裝都掉)<br />\n星期二、五：冰龍(掉甲)<br />\n星期三、六：雷龍(掉頭)<br />\n星期日：暗龍(掉武器、亦都係最多人刷)<br />\n星期一、二58級以上協力：武器<br />\n星期五、六58級以上協力：頭同甲<br />\n<br />\n職業精通石：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModfFKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModfFKV.jpg&h=45612769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭生命都係250<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊有咩抽？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.needgames.tw/m/share.php?page=articlepage&amp;id=182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.needgames.tw%2Fm%2Fshare.php%3Fpage%3Darticlepage%26id%3D182&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=74de67d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.needgames.tw/m/share.php?page=articlepage&amp;id=182</a><br />\n<br />\n真女主白毛澤瑞達<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELjCQsd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELjCQsd.jpg&h=f10542b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZfKvsd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZfKvsd.jpg&h=768c5a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老婆油膩鴨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3XnPH7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3XnPH7r.png&h=3c882725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b594fbe4267dc838ddb0c61c0ce5dcf07166d8dd","tid":2448451,"uid":7550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d123dcbc1c01d345c0da2e7222fdb584522d25ce","tid":2448451,"uid":112128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"咸魚留名"},{"pid":"42c61ec892d330380131c134a5222f0890e8a8e6","tid":2448451,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"鹹魚留名"},{"pid":"1d3e6302fb80a6b8a8a7ae628ba9c194f496bedb","tid":2448451,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"abffafdec20e9e5ebda3aa3fe4e8b2ef186aacdc","tid":2448451,"uid":23957,"like":0,"dis